ygData.messageBody:
I forgot to report that I have payed close attention to all your suggestions
for where to fight with Tsengu.

Tsengu spent all of 10 in North Karana at the spires. Great zone for a
youngun, a nice place to hang with higher levels too for advice,buying and
selling and drive-by buffings.

11-12.25 has been Kurns Tower as I reported. One nice thing about the
skellies is that quite often they drop 2-4 gold, which is a lot for a level
10-12 mob. When you get bored you can go outside and look for bugs/exiles.
It is starting to get a bit long in the tooth however, I think it may be
time soon to be off to Unrest. I just can't miss it again.

One note on the Kicsh, when I said i would wait till 19 to go get it I was
assuming it was still NO DROP and I might be able to loot it if I was
patient. Since it isn't....I think it will be a while longer :o)

Tszaaz/Tsengu


[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
